Product description

Game Menu

Story
This single play mode allows you to enjoy the main story written down for this project. In this mode, the story goes through with the "Haku" and clears the stage. Clear conditions are different for each stage and the "purposes" are updated with every event progressed, so you can continue to review them and progress in stories.

Offline Match Online
Players can play on each other offline or online. Up to 4 players and sometimes the computer replaces the player. Final Purpose, Clear Conditions, and Map Selection are possible, so you can play against the player's situation. "Stamps" are available for online matching communication tool. Various stamps are available for fun play.

Game Flow
You can decide what you set to victory conditions. We aim to achieve victory conditions while fighting with chemical and other players through the trout that stops, as well as rule villages, shopping, and acquiring treasure chests. You can play with it in a variety of ways such as cooperation and interruption.

Character
This product has RPG elements, so you can decrease the animal and other objects to improve the level of the character, and learn the skill. Also, each character has different skills to learn, so you can get the advantage of your game when you play battle and action, using your skills.

Model Number: HAC-P-ATRSA(JPN)

From the Manufacturer

The world of "Uchakaon" has become a RPG style board game "Docapon".

Docapon's latest production that has been sold in many home gaming consoles as a fairly type board game with RPG elements, has been released in a vibrant set of the world of Utakuru One.

The stages and items are all built according to the world of "Utaru Ones", and the characters from the "Utararu On" series are not only playable characters, but also adventure parts and play stories.

With the "story" mode that you can enjoy the main story in full voice, the "offline match" that you can enjoy gathering with friends at home as you want, and the "online match" online match" that is the first consumer version of the "Docapon" series, you can play with both friends and more.

Story

This single play mode allows you to enjoy the main story written down for this project.

In this mode, the story goes through with the "Haku" and clears the stage.

Clear conditions are different for each stage and the "purposes" are updated with every event progressed, so you can continue to review them and progress in stories.

Battle Mode

Players can play on each other offline or online.

Up to 4 players and sometimes the computer replaces the player.

Final Purpose, Clear Conditions, and Map Selection are possible, so you can play against the player's circumstances.

"Stamps" are available for online matching communication tool.Various stamps are available for fun play.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
